# Backend — Spring Boot 4 (Kotlin)

## Stack
- Spring Boot 4.0.x, Kotlin 2.2+, Java 21
- Spring Security OAuth2 Client + JWT
- Spring Data JPA + Flyway migrations
- Jackson 3.x, JUnit Jupiter 6
- Azure Container Apps deployment

## Structure
```
src/main/kotlin/{{ package_identifier | replace('.', '/') }}/
  config/       → SecurityConfig, WebConfig, OAuth2Config
  common/       → ApiException, GlobalExceptionHandler, PagedResponse
  auth/         → AuthController, AuthService, JwtTokenProvider, User entity
  features/     → Feature modules (controller/service/repository/entity/dto)
```

## Patterns
- Controller → Service → Repository → Entity
- DTOs separate from entities (Request/Response suffixed)
- Global exception handler returns `ApiErrorResponse`
- Pagination via `Pageable` → `PagedResponse<T>`
- All endpoints require JWT except `/auth/**`
- Flyway migrations in `src/main/resources/db/migration/`
- Tests use `@SpringBootTest` + MockK

## Commands
- `./gradlew bootRun` or `task backend:run`
- `./gradlew test` or `task backend:test`
- `./gradlew assembleBootDist` or `task backend:build`
